item.title: Check out the awesome BarCamp logo
item.description: I’m not exaggerating when I say I think it’s the best BarCamp logo I’ve ever seen! John Henry Donovan has done a perfect mash-up of the classic logo with the outline of Cork. Thanks John Henry, looking forward to meeting you in Cork.
